devdoc.details: This library is developed for modularity purposes and because at the time of developing (Feb 2023), in Solidity, the maximum size of a contract is restricted to 24 KB

getApiOnCoveragePayable(SharedStructs.Co.details: Balance is the caller Contract's balance. It should always be equal to the payment the consumers gave on the function call.- -It should not accumulate ether. Then, the Contract pays equally the API consumers' addresses the amount it recieved on call.
